{
  "stem": "5795.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I've been out in the German street the first time in five years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SPEAKING YIDDISH] I said, what do you mean?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means, I couldn't kill them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh my God, what's happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Haven't you heard of the gas chambers?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, I have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Have you heard of the crematoria?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, I have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They murdered us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They murdered my own parents in front of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people, kids, I saw in the street, young men and women-- they kicked us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They spat on us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I couldn't kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he had-- I said, has he killed them?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "How do I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then the magic words that I've been waiting for-- because the officers kept saying to me, Padre, what are you crying for?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What you're doing, they're not-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they may not be worth keeping alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "How can they be normal after going through this hell of hells?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, give them a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Give them a chance, as I believe the Jew is born civilized.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That no matter they tried to destroy us, we-- as long as we're on our feet, we'll, we'll jump.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll come back again into our own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I rushed to the major.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I've got my postman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told him this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I go to the unit and the tailor there, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I give him a, a battle dress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was too, too big for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he wouldn't let me take it off his shoulders-- nah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he went around, got it sent out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
